data.description: Welcome to this 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom split foyer in NW Lincoln. The main floor boasts three bedrooms, a full bathroom, a spacious living room, and an eat-in kitchen equipped with all-new appliances, including a range hood. The dining area features a large sliding door that opens to an expansive deck, perfect for outdoor relaxation. In the basement, you'll find a recreation room and a 3/4 bathroom, along with a laundry room and storage space. The backyard, graced with a beautiful deck and flourishing pear trees, offers an ideal retreat. There's also a generously sized shed with storage shelves for your outdoor projects. The driveway has been expanded to provide extra parking space, adding to your convenience. This home is located near shopping, restaurants, and provides easy access to highways.
